#iBeacon detection setting
1. import CoreBluetooth and CoreLocation framework.
2. Add NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription and NSLocationWhenInUsageDescription in your info.plist.
3. Add App Transport Security in your info.plist and set it to Yes.
4. Add [self.locationManager requestAlwayAuthorization] and [self.locationManager requestWhenInUseAuthorization] in your ViewController's viewDidLoad section.
